verbose_text: It reproduces experimental measurements of 8 entities (total amount of procaspase-8, its cleaved product p43 / p41, caspase-8, procaspase-3, caspase-3, IkappaB-alpha, phosphorylated IkappaB-alpha and cleaved p43-FLIP) obtained using Western blot technology for HeLa cells stably overexpressing CD95-GFP and treated with three different concentrations of agonistic anti-CD95 antibodies (1500, 500 and 250 ng/ml).
